KIjai nodes,from:
https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes
How to use:
Right-click to load an image; click "new canvas" to clear; hold down the Shift key and left-click to input positive points (green dots), right-click to input negative points (red dots); hold the mouse button to drag points, right-click on a point to delete it. Note that the first and last points cannot be deleted; hold down Ctrl, and hold the left button to draw a bounding box (bbox).
